@using ContractAndProjectManager.Helpers
@using ContractAndProjectManager.Entities
@using ContractAndProjectManager.Models
@using ContractAndProjectManager.Data
@using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore
@model ContractAndProjectManager.Entities.Project
@inject ApplicationContext DbContext;

@{
    var projectStatuses = SelectListHelpers.CreateSelectList(ProjectStatus.All, x => new SelectListModel
    {
        Id = x.Id,
        Title = x.Name
    }, Model.Status?.StatusId ?? 0);

    var analytics = await DbContext.ProjectAnalytics.FirstOrDefaultAsync(x => x.ProjectId == Model.Id);
    var stageIds = Model.Stages.Select(x => x.Id);
    var stageAnalytics = await DbContext.ProjectStageAnalytics.Where(x => stageIds.Contains(x.ProjectStageId)).ToListAsync();

}

<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
    <h3 class="text text-primary">@Model.Name</h3>
    <form asp-area="TeamLead" asp-controller="Project" asp-action="SetStatus">
        <input hidden name="projectId" value="@Model.Id"/>
        <input hidden name="returnToHome" value="true"/>
        <select onchange="this.form.submit()" style="border-color: @Model.Status?.Status.Color" name="statusId" class="custom-select" asp-items="projectStatuses"></select>
    </form>
</div>

<p class="text">@Model.Description</p>

<div class="grid-default grid-default-2 mb-2">
    <p class="m-0 text" style="color: @Model.Status?.Status.Color">@Model.Status?.Status.Name</p>
    @if (Model.DateStart != null && Model?.Status?.Status.Id == ProjectStatus.Pending.Id)
    {
        <p class="m-0 text-success" style="color: @Model.Status.Status.Color">Дата начала - @DateHelpers.DateFormat(Model.DateStart.Value, true)</p>
    }
    @if (Model.DateDeadLine != null)
    {
        <p class="m-0 text-info">Дедлайн - @DateHelpers.DateFormat(Model.DateDeadLine.Value, true)</p>
    }
</div>

<div class="card mb-2">
    <div class="card-header">
        Аналитика
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="grid-default grid-default-2">
            <p class="text text-dark m-0">Суммарно времени - @(analytics.TotalHours?.ToString("0.0")) ч</p>
            <p class="text text-dark m-0">Этапов - @analytics.StagesCount</p>
            <p class="text text-dark m-0">Всего задач - @analytics.TasksCount</p>
            <p class="text text-dark m-0">Выполнено задач - @analytics.DoneTasksCount</p>
            <p class="text text-dark m-0">Действующих сотрудников - @analytics.EmployeesCount</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@foreach (var item in Model.Contract.Stages)
{
    <div class="card mb-2">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                <p class="text m-0">@item.Title</p>
                <p class="m-0 text" style="opacity: 0.7">Этап договора</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid-default grid-default-2 mt-2">
                @if (item.DateStart != null)
                {
                    <p class="m-0 text-success" style="color: @Model.Status.Status.Color">Дата начала - @DateHelpers.DateFormat(item.DateStart.Value, true)</p>
                }
                @if (item.DateDeadLine != null)
                {
                    <p class="m-0 text-info">Дата окончания - @DateHelpers.DateFormat(item.DateDeadLine.Value, true)</p>
                }
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="list-group">
                @if (item.ProjectStages.Count == 0)
                {
                    <p class="text m-0">Нет связанных этапов проекта</p>
                }
                else
                {
                    @foreach (var stage in item.ProjectStages)
                    {
                        var sa = stageAnalytics.FirstOrDefault(x => x.ProjectStageId == stage.Id);

                        <div class="list-group-item">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                <h5 class="m-0">@stage.Title</h5>
                                <div>
                                    <div class="btn-group btn-group-sm">
                                        <a class="btn btn-outline-danger" asp-area="TeamLead" asp-controller="ProjectStage" asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@stage.Id">Удалить</a>
                                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" asp-area="TeamLead" asp-controller="ProjectStage" asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@stage.Id">Изменить</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mb-1" style="opacity: 0.75">Ответственный - @stage.Executor?.Name</p>
                            @if (stage.Description != null)
                            {
                                <p class="m-0">@stage.Description</p>
                            }

                            @if (sa != null)
                            {
                                <hr class="my-2"/>
                                <h6>Аналитика</h6>
                                <div class="grid-default grid-default-2">
                                    @if (sa.TotalHours != null)
                                    {
                                        <p class="text text-dark m-0">Суммарно времени - @(sa.TotalHours?.ToString("0.0")) ч</p>
                                    }
                                    <p class="text text-dark m-0">Всего задач - @sa.TasksCount</p>
                                    <p class="text text-dark m-0">Выполнено задач - @sa.DoneTasksCount</p>
                                    <p class="text text-dark m-0">Зайдествовано сотрудников - @sa.EmployeesCount</p>
                                </div>
                            }


                            <div class="card border-primary mt-2">
                                <div class="card-header p-2">Задачи</div>
                                <div class="card-body p-2">
                                    <div class="list-group mb-2">
                                        @foreach (var task in stage.Tasks)
                                        {
                                            <div class="list-group-item" style="border-left: 3px solid @task.Status?.Status.Color">
                                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                                    <h6>@task.Title</h6>
                                                    <div class="btn-group btn-group-sm">
                                                        <a class="btn btn-outline-danger" asp-area="TeamLead" asp-controller="Task" asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@task.Id">Удалить</a>
                                                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" asp-area="TeamLead" asp-controller="Task" asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@task.Id">Изменить</a>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="grid-default grid-default-2 my-1">
                                                    <p class="m-0 text" style="color: @task.Status?.Status.Color">
                                                        <span class="text-dark">Статус -</span> @task.Status?.Status.Name
                                                    </p>
                                                    @if (task.Executor != null)
                                                    {
                                                        <p class="m-0 text">Исполнитель - @task.Executor.Name</p>
                                                    }
                                                </div>
                                                @if (task.DateStart != null || task.DateDeadLine != null)
                                                {
                                                    <div class="grid-default grid-default-2 my-1">
                                                        @if (task.DateStart != null)
                                                        {
                                                            <p class="m-0 text-success" style="color: @Model.Status.Status.Color">Дата начала - @DateHelpers.DateFormat(task.DateStart.Value, true)</p>
                                                        }
                                                        @if (task.DateDeadLine != null)
                                                        {
                                                            <p class="m-0 text-info">Дата завершения - @DateHelpers.DateFormat(task.DateDeadLine.Value, true)</p>
                                                        }
                                                    </div>
                                                }
                                                @if (task.Description != null)
                                                {
                                                    <p class="m-0">@task.Description</p>
                                                }
                                            </div>
                                        }
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="">
                                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm" asp-area="TeamLead" asp-controller="Task" asp-action="Create" asp-route-projectStageId="@stage.Id">Добавить задачу</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
                <div class="mt-2">
                    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" asp-area="TeamLead" asp-controller="ProjectStage" asp-action="Create" asp-route-contractStageId="@item.Id">Добавить этап</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
}